	(text "Calcumaker 16 main — Annunciator LEDs (DESIGN.md status-line mapping). PLACED, not wired. Five MCU GPIOs (active high), each -> Rn 470R -> LED -> GND: D61 'f' yellow + D62 'g' blue mounted BESIDE the f/g keys; D63 'C' carry, D64 'G' overflow, D65 low-battery along the top edge under the display bezel. 470R @3V3 = ~1.3-2.8mA; adjust per color at bring-up. Firmware: calcumaker-core App drives f/g from keys::Shift, C/G from Calc::carry()/overflow(); LOWBAT from the battery ADC (PSU). Radix/STATUS/errors render in the digits."
		(exclude_from_sim no)
		(at 15.00 105.00 0)
		(effects (font (size 1.5 1.5)) (justify left top))
		(uuid "c6a90ddb-56e6-4c67-8ff9-4631954946c2")
